          "reviewBody": "Two years in a row CIS accepted an application for my daughter knowing full well that there were no slots at all available, taking 16,000 rupees in non-refundable application fees each time. When I finally managed to meet with someone I was told snottily “we haven’t had openings in those grade levels for years…”\n\nThis is fraudulent behaviour and should not be allowed.",
