            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This is the most greediest school's in the world, I would rather say the management is the worst.They have simply charged us 15k for my daughter's admission form and without even taking any assessment, management just denied saying she doesn't qualify, education council of India should not recommend such high fees for admission form unless the child  is getting through without even reviewing  my daughter's  application they have decided  not to give her admission\n. I'm so blessed that  my daughter didn't get thru such greedy management and the lady Elizabeth Anthony  is the rudest.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
