            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "No extra stress on anything. Academics is dealt with in a very simple but effective way. they pay attention to the students dreams and what they want to do. Balance between extra-curricular activities and academics is perfect. Even though the school is not in the is not the most affordable place, it is worth it.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
